"<comment>(もちろんalsa-libはただの例です)</comment>\n"
"# <i>emerge -vp alsa-lib</i>\n"
"[ebuild  N    ] media-libs/alsa-lib-1.0.14_rc1  -debug +doc 698 kB\n"

